Package com.bean

Class Policy

java.lang.Object
com.bean.Policy
public class Policy extends Object
The Policy class represents a vehicle insurance policy. It includes details such as the policy number, vehicle information, customer details, insurance type, premium amount, coverage dates, and the underwriter ID.
